sophical career, Ultimate Questions is a deeply personal meditation on the meaning of life and the ways we should live and face death.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Mai 2019) 0aHuman beings. 0aOntology. 0aPhilosophical anthropology. 0aPhilosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Ethics & Moral Philosophy.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPUP eBook-Package Pilot Project 2016z978311063859240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781400880454zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781400880454.jpg  a978-3-11-063859-2  PUP eBook-Package Pilot Project 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA21UPPPUP  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG  aPDA9PRIN